### OrderFormModal

**Location**: [`src/components/orders/OrderFormModal.tsx`](../src/components/orders/OrderFormModal.tsx)

**Purpose**: Bulk order creation interface with multi-part support and VIN validation.

**Features**:
- Single or batch order entry
